# Generated TypeScript proto output is regenerable via `make proto`.
# NOTE: gen/go is intentionally TRACKED — it is a build-critical, hand-
# maintained Go module that services depend on via `replace ../../gen/go`
# and that the Docker builds COPY. Ignoring it broke clone-to-run.
gen/ts/

